{"tid":2166433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員套指模程序出錯 律政司指警方已嚴厲訓斥 官質疑：上司教得唔好就冇事？","createTime":"2020-08-20T12:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T14:49:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":377,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"b086b54f268729afe8224abf245d4cf0689653e2","tid":2166433,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/LUYOFMH43JB5VDGVBQVVFFGOXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FLUYOFMH43JB5VDGVBQVVFFGOXY%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5Z1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=ec3a9074\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FLUYOFMH43JB5VDGVBQVVFFGOXY%2F&h=2e7eb025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/LUYOFMH43JB5VDGVBQVVFFGOXY/</a><br />\n<br />\n騙案積犯早前被定罪，惟案件早前在區域法院判刑時，控方聲稱因被告多次拒絕打手指模，警方無法取得其新近刑事罪行紀錄，惹來法官葉佐文不滿。律政司代表今到庭解畫，稱警方將會發出內部便箋，提醒警員其實可用武力檢取指模，並已「嚴厲訓斥」涉事警員。惟葉官聞言卻替被訓斥的警員不值，謂：「缺乏經驗就被訓斥，上司教佢做嘢做得唔好就冇事，我覺得有啲唔公平囉。」"},{"pid":"34043a0027e47a36543130d99eeac39970765999","tid":2166433,"uid":362346,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"-.-"},{"pid":"b36b33f48ce24d247f494fb5de649f310c22b699","tid":2166433,"uid":307203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5922b7609b8c282206d2e85d4ab198f01843b214","tid":2166433,"uid":216344,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"34043a0027e47a36543130d99eeac39970765999","tid":2166433,"uid":362346,"like":17,"disl